name: Top Products by Revenue Query
query:
SELECT
    shopee_product.item_name AS product_name,
    SUM(shopee_order_item.qty) AS qty,
    SUM(shopee_order_item.model_discounted_price * shopee_order_item.qty) AS total_revenue
FROM 
    `tabShopee Order Item` AS shopee_order_item INNER JOIN
    `tabShopee Order` AS shopee_order ON shopee_order_item.parent = shopee_order.name INNER JOIN 
    `tabShopee Product` AS shopee_product ON shopee_order_item.shopee_product = shopee_product.name
GROUP BY
    shopee_product.item_name
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC
;
